<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head><meta charset="utf-8"></head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f7f7f5;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei','PingFang SC',Arial,sans-serif;">
<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#f7f7f5;"><tr><td align="center" style="padding:20px 10px;">
<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width:600px;background:#ffffff;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);">

  <tr><td style="background:#334155;padding:16px 24px;color:#fff;">
    <div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;">QBU 日报运行运维日志{% if severity is defined and severity %} · {{ severity }}{% endif %}</div>
    <div style="font-size:11px;opacity:0.75;margin-top:4px;">{{ logical_date }} · run #{{ run_id }}</div>
  </td></tr>

  <tr><td style="padding:20px 24px;">
    <p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-size:13px;color:#1a1a2e;line-height:1.6;">
      日报运行过程中出现需要技术侧跟进的采集或通知信号。该邮件只用于运维追踪，不代表业务报告结论。
      请优先查看随信附件中的 run log，再结合服务端日志判断是否需要重跑或修复配置。
    </p>
    {% if ops_summary is defined and ops_summary %}
    <p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-size:12px;color:#334155;line-height:1.6;background:#f8fafc;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:6px;padding:10px;">
      {{ ops_summary | replace('\n', '<br>') | safe }}
    </p>
    {% endif %}
    {% if run_log_path is defined and run_log_path %}
    <p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-size:11px;color:#64748b;line-height:1.6;">
      运行日志：<span style="font-family:monospace;">{{ run_log_path }}</span>
    </p>
    {% endif %}

    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;font-size:12px;margin-top:8px;">
      <tr style="background:#f0efed;color:#555770;">
        <td style="padding:8px 10px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px 0 0 0;">字段</td>
        <td style="padding:8px 10px;font-weight:700;text-align:center;">缺失数</td>
        <td style="padding:8px 10px;font-weight:700;text-align:center;border-radius:0 4px 0 0;">缺失率</td>
      </tr>
      {% for label, key_n, key_r in [
          ("rating",        "missing_rating",        "missing_rating_ratio"),
          ("stock_status",  "missing_stock",         "missing_stock_ratio"),
          ("review_count",  "missing_review_count",  "missing_review_count_ratio"),
      ] %}
      {% set ratio = quality.get(key_r, 0.0) %}
      <tr>
        <td style="padding:8px 10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e4e0;color:#1a1a2e;">{{ label }}</td>
        <td style="padding:8px 10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e4e0;text-align:center;font-family:monospace;">{{ quality.get(key_n, 0) }}</td>
        <td style="padding:8px 10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e4e0;text-align:center;font-weight:700;color:{% if ratio >= threshold %}#b91c1c{% else %}#8e8ea0{% endif %};">{{ '%.1f' % (ratio * 100) }}%</td>
      </tr>
      {% endfor %}
    </table>

    {# F011 Critical B-1: defensive checks. Legacy quality dicts (pre-F011)
       lack these v3 fields. Use ``quality.get(...)`` so missing keys produce
       a falsy ``None`` instead of Jinja ``Undefined``, which would crash on
       numeric comparisons (``Undefined < 0.6``) and on ``is not none``. #}
    {% set _zero_skus = quality.get('zero_scrape_skus') %}
    {% set _completeness = quality.get('scrape_completeness_ratio') %}
    {% set _deadletter = quality.get('outbox_deadletter_count') %}
    {% set _est_date = quality.get('estimated_date_ratio') %}
    {% if _zero_skus or _deadletter or _est_date or _completeness is not none %}
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;font-size:12px;margin-top:12px;">
      {% if _zero_skus %}
      <tr>
        <td style="padding:6px 10px;color:#b91c1c;font-weight:700;">P0 · 零采集 SKU</td>
        <td style="padding:6px 10px;text-align:right;font-family:monospace;color:#1a1a2e;">
          {{ _zero_skus|length }} 个：{{ _zero_skus[:5]|join(', ') }}{% if _zero_skus|length > 5 %} …{% endif %}
        </td>
      </tr>
      {% endif %}
      {% if _completeness is not none %}
      <tr>
        <td style="padding:6px 10px;color:#1a1a2e;">采集完整率</td>
        <td style="padding:6px 10px;text-align:right;font-family:monospace;font-weight:700;color:{% if _completeness < 0.6 %}#b91c1c{% else %}#1a1a2e{% endif %};">
          {{ '%.1f' % (_completeness * 100) }}%
        </td>
      </tr>
      {% endif %}
      {% if _deadletter %}
      <tr>
        <td style="padding:6px 10px;color:#b45309;font-weight:700;">P1 · 通知 deadletter</td>
        <td style="padding:6px 10px;text-align:right;font-family:monospace;">{{ _deadletter }} 条</td>
      </tr>
      {% endif %}
      {% if _est_date %}
      <tr>
        <td style="padding:6px 10px;color:#8e8ea0;">估算日期占比</td>
        <td style="padding:6px 10px;text-align:right;font-family:monospace;color:{% if _est_date > 0.3 %}#b45309{% else %}#8e8ea0{% endif %};">
          {{ '%.1f' % (_est_date * 100) }}%
        </td>
      </tr>
      {% endif %}
    </table>
    {% endif %}

    <p style="margin:12px 0 0;font-size:11px;color:#8e8ea0;line-height:1.6;">
      该邮件由运行守护自动发出，不等于业务数据变动。业务报告和业务变动邮件另行推送。
    </p>
  </td></tr>

</table>
</td></tr></table>
</body></html>
